value:
Familiarisation programs are carried out by way of exhaustive
presentations on various topics and areas like
1. Overall industry in which the Company operates, Company’s
operations and Strategy and Annual Budget of the Company;
2. Financials;
3. Statutory Compliance;
4. Annual Report;
5. Company Policies;
6. Cost Records;
7. Corporate Social Responsibilities framework;
8. Enterprise Risk Management;
9. Regulatory updates at Board and Audit Committee Meetings;
and
10. Investor Grievances etc.

